snippet.title: Is it Better to Walk or Run in the Rain?
snippet.description:
Subscribe to MinutePhysics - it's FREE! http://dft.ba/-minutephysics_sub

For recent scientific publications on the walk/rain question: http://iopscience.iop.org/0143-0807/33/5/1321

MinutePhysics is on Google+ - http://bit.ly/qzEwc6 
And facebook - http://facebook.com/minutephysics
And twitter - @minutephysics

Minute Physics provides an energetic and entertaining view of old and new problems in physics -- all in a minute!
